1) vim /etc/apt/sources.list

#~~~~~~Jessie~~~~~~#

deb http://ftp.pl.debian.org/debian/ testing main non-free contrib
deb-src http://ftp.pl.debian.org/debian/ testing main non-free contrib
deb http://security.debian.org/ testing/updates main contrib non-free
deb-src http://security.debian.org/ testing/updates main contrib non-free

#~~~~~~Deb-multimedia~~~~~~#

deb http://www.deb-multimedia.org/ testing main non-free
deb-src http://www.deb-multimedia.org/ testing main non-free


2) aptitude update && aptitude dist-upgrade (jeśli w virtualbox, to także aptitude install virtualbox-guest-x11)

3) aptitude install xserver-xorg xinit openbox slim
4) startx
* dpkg-reconfigure xserver-xorg
